Example: Servlet-FileUpload
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
You can access the Web application from your browser:

URL: http://lab.se.org:8080/Servlet-FileUpload


How to run the example?
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

$ mvn wildfly:deploy

Make sure that you have a /home/student/tmp folder!!!
$ pwd
/home/student
$ mkdir tmp


